doc.title: porogaramuw dilanni
doc.description: Nin yɔrɔ in bɛ kuma porogaramu kɛcogo kan

example1.title: {{0}}So ɲɛ kode misali
example1.annotation1: A dɔn ni a ye domani tɔgɔ fɔlɔ kelen ye Ni o tɛ, i ka segin {{0}} kan ani i kana baara kɛ tugun.
example1.annotation2: A dɔn ni {{0}} ye walima ni kanal ka daminɛyɔrɔ ye A sira bɛ daminɛ ni @ taamasiyɛn ye.
example1.annotation3: A dɔn ni a ye wideyo ɲɛ ye.
example1.annotation4: A dɔn ni a ye wideyo ɲɛ surun ye.
